\begin_layout Section
Conclusions
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We have made several attempts at reconciling the measured opacities with
 the ATM+bandpass model.
 Nothing works! except if we accept to modify the 2
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

mm continuum water vapour emissivity upward by a 1.55 factor.
 The 1
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

mm emissivity must be left untouched.
 This discussion does not address the opacity ratio observed between array
 1 and 3 at 1
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

mm.
\end_layout

